title: Phir Aur Kya Chahiye| Zara Hatke Zara Bachke| Vicky K, Sara Ali K, Arijit Singh,Sachin-Jigar,Amitabh
description:
Lose yourself in the magic of love with the much-awaited song "Phir Aur Kya Chahiye'' from the film 'Zara Hatke Zara Bachke'. Mesmerizing vocals of Arijit Singh perfectly complement the intense chemistry between Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal. The music is composed by the talented duo Sachin-Jigar, and is here to make your heart skip a beat!

The soulful lyrics penned by Amitabh Bhattacharya will make you feel the love. A must watch movie directed by Laxman Utekar, featuring Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal.

title: Ostrich in Space - AutoRigging a Blender Model with Character Creator 4 and iClone 8
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/auto-rig.html 
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/blender.html Get ready to soar into space with the help of 3D character designer Tom Breuer! In this insightful YouTube video, Breuer shares his streamlined workflow for creating a super fly ostrich that's out of this world, using the powerful combination of Character Creator, Blender, and iClone. With the lightning-fast CC AccuRIG tool, you can turbocharge your character preparation process for animation and customize auto-rigging steps that give you complete creative control. 

Plus, you can easily add spring bones and cloth simulation to make your animated accessories even more awesome! And with AccuLips, precise lip-sync animation has never been easier. So buckle up and get ready for an epic ride as Breuer takes you on a journey through the Reallusion-Blender pipeline, proving that anything is possible when you create your own little world! https://magazine.reallusion.com/2023/04/19/ostrich-in-space-autorigging-a-blender-model-with-character-creator-4-and-iclone-8/

00:00 Opening
00:17 Character Concept
00:33 Modeling Process
01:29 Texturing in Substance Painter
01:55 Rigging with CC AccuRIG in Character Creator
03:10 Adding Custom Bones in Blender
04:00 Skin Weight Transfer
04:57 Adding More Bones in Blender & Character Creator
05:10 Making Facial Expressions
06:29 Animating Dynamic Accessories in Character Creator: Adding Spring Bones & Cloth Simulation
07:38 Animating in iClone
08:34 Create Animated Accessories: Adding Spring Bones
09:06 Animation Clips & Lip-Sync Animation with AccuLips 
09:26 Wrap-Up & Final Animation

*Tom Breuer* is a dynamic and talented freelance 3D designer with a particular flair for Blender and Unity in game-based applications and character creation. With ardent storytelling, he has created a whole world filled with fascinating 3D creatures with unique backstories that he loves to share. You can explore Breuer's stunning creatures thriving in their natural habitats by visiting his pages listed below.

â–ª Sketchfab: https://sketchfab.com/TomBreuer
â–ª ArtStation: https://www.artstation.com/flyingillustration
â–ª Twitter: https://twitter.com/flyingillu
â–ª Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/flyingillustration/

Voice actor of Ostrich: *Vincent Fallow*
â–ª Twitter: https://twitter.com/vincentfallow
â–ª Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/vincentfallow/

Character Creator 4 (CC4) connects industry leading pipelines ,such as iClone, Maya, Blender, Unreal Engine, Unity, with one system for 3D character generation, animation rig, asset management, look-dev rendering, and interactive design.

iClone is the fastest real-time 3D animation software in the industry. Integrated with groundbreaking real-time technologies, iClone simplifies the world of 3D Animation in a user-friendly production environment that blends character animation, scene design and cinematic storytelling; quickly turning imagination into a reality.

Kya Loge Tum | Akshay Kumar | Amyra Dastur | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
description:
Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

The emotionally charged lyrics written by Jaani, along with his heart-wrenching composition, add an extra layer of depth to the already powerful track produced by B Praak himself. Arvindr Khaira takes it to the next level with his visionary direction, featuring Akshay Kumar and Amyra Dastur's palpable chemistry that will leave you wanting more.

description:
https://www.reallusion.com/auto-setup/unity/default.html

Experienced 3D artist Jasper Hesseling shares his iClone-to-Unity workflow, using the Auto Setup plugin to seamlessly transfer his CC4-based character, Lynn, to Unity for HDRP rendering with realistic digital human shaders. By leveraging the animation previews in Unity Auto Setup and Reallusion's Parkour motion pack, he creates an impressive action sequence, complete with lifelike facial expressions.

In this video, Jasper guides viewers through each critical step and provides valuable insights into creating his â€œsecret agentâ€. He showcases the versatility of the Character Creator pipeline and also incorporates other powerful 3D tools such as Marvelous Designer, Substance Painter, KitBash3D, Cascadeur, and ZBrush.

title: Outro Lite
Meet â€œSusanâ€, a Realistic Digital Human with Dynamic Wrinkles | Character Creator & iClone
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/dynamic-wrinkle.html
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/3d-content.html Toy with three hyper-realistic CC4 avatars, â€œSusanâ€, â€œKevinâ€, and â€œCamilaâ€, while wielding the power of dynamic wrinkles and extended facial profiles. Backed by more than 140 morphs, these characters are completely free to use in Character Creator 4 and iClone 8. Susan is the perfect example of Reallusionâ€™s Mesh-to-CC technology that can accurately map original scan models from TexturingXYZ onto CC3+ character meshes. Learn to use the illustrious tools in iClone like Face Puppet, Face Key Editor, and Live Face to adjust facial expressions. Live Face, in particular, is a free facial mocap application that is robust and packed with features.

With the advanced real-time blended dynamic wrinkles and look-at constraints, Susan can seamlessly perform lip-sync animation with natural body movements and facial nuances. Users can take advantage of Character Creator 4 and iClone 8 to personalize over 300 expression morphs with modeling sliders. Plus, all styling and makeup content listed below comes included with the software. Access a wealth of options from the Reallusion asset collections, including 3D hair, skin textures, and clothes, to create unique stories for Susan.

*I.Embedded FREE dynamic wrinkles*
â–ª 2 Individualized Wrinkles: Susan | Kevin 
â–ª 2 Generalized Wrinkles: Neutral | Camila

*II.Embedded FREE content*
â–ª Atmosphere and Lightroom: 100+ presets

â–ª Preview Animations: 40+ Preview Motions

â–ª Hair: 10+ styles

â–ª Skin: 90+ presets
â–ª Makeup: 70+ presets

Find out more resource on our Forum post â€œWhere to Find New Wrinkle Assetsâ€: https://forum.reallusion.com/532894/Character-Creator-42-Arrived-Where-to-Find-New-Wrinkle-Assets-Free-Embedded-Content 

Character Creator 4 (CC4) connects industry leading pipelines ,such as iClone, Maya, Blender, Unreal Engine, Unity, with one system for 3D character generation, animation rig, asset management, look-dev rendering, and interactive design.

iClone is the fastest real-time 3D animation software in the industry. Integrated with groundbreaking real-time technologies, iClone simplifies the world of 3D Animation in a user-friendly production environment that blends character animation, scene design and cinematic storytelling; quickly turning imagination into a reality.

title: VERIVERY - 'Crazy Like That' Official M/V
description:
VERIVERY â€“ A Trendy Icon Acknowledged by All
With the release of [Liminality â€“ EP.LOVE] last November, VERIVERY had managed to sweep multiple awards from ceremonies on top of achieving first place on music programs.

And in May 2023, VERIVERY returns with their second story through [Liminality â€“ EP.DREAM].
 
DREAM: The Second Element of Happiness
In [Liminality â€“ EP.LOVE], VERIVERY had expressed the emotion of â€˜loveâ€™ through a number of different ways. This time, through [Liminality â€“ EP.DREAM], VERIVERY shows off their intuitive, unique colors in the process of achieving their DREAM.

To PLAY in the Present, or PLAN for the Future
VERIVERY plans to show two different paths towards their DREAM.
With the â€˜PLAYâ€™ version emphasizing oneâ€™s happiness in the moment, and â€˜PLANâ€™ version focusing on meticulously preparing for their future, the members will appeal to all through two contrasting sides.
The jacket expresses the journey towards a DREAM through both a â€˜PLAYâ€™-focused path, bringing energy to a chaotic yet humble space, and a â€˜PLANâ€™-focused path, where building a blueprint for the future is portrayed in a mature, intellectual way. 
As well, the music video shows the members striving towards their DREAM in both unrestrained strides and steady, passionate steps to show the qualities unique to each of the two paths. As each of their individual spaces come together to create a common area, the members also come together in making the achievement of their DREAM a common goal.

Liminality - EP. DREAM, the Expansion of VERIVERY
Through the [Liminality - EP.DREAM] album, VERIVERY brings to light their ever-expanding musical spectrum. Through new styles of music, performance, and visuals, the group promises to show off yet another distinct, artistic side to them.
VERIVERY welcomes all into their space filled with their DREAM, so that we could all step into and explore their â€˜DREAMâ€™ home using their unique key.

title: Vegan TAQUITOS That Are Baked And Full Of Flavor!
description:
Crispy vegan baked taquitos which are super easy to make, gluten-free, and delicious. These meat-free flautas are filled with a hearty veggie mixture that is bursting with flavor. Enjoy this simple rolled taco recipe as a snack, dinner or side dish! ğŸ˜

Printable recipe with instructions, substitutes, nutrition facts, and lots of helpful tips:
https://elavegan.com/easy-vegan-taquitos/

ğŸ“© Want FREE RECIPES and meal plans delivered to your inbox? Sign up for my newsletter at no cost ğŸ‘‰ https://tinyurl.com/elavegan

ğŸ“– My cookbook "Simple and Delicious Vegan" is out! I poured my heart and soul into this cookbook, and it contains many of my best recipes that I created over the last 7 years! It has:

ğŸŒ± 100 vegan AND gluten-free recipes for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and dessert, including sides, snacks, soups, sauces, salads, and bread - all with beautiful pictures, I took myself!
ğŸŒ± Metric and imperial measurements (cups, ounces, and grams).
ğŸŒ± Refined sugar-free and allergy-friendly recipes with substitutions for any irritating ingredients.
ğŸŒ± Ingredient shots, so you see what to buy - getting you cooking - and eating - faster!

You can order it here: https://elavegan.com/cookbooks/

INGREDIENTS:
 
2 medium-large (400 g) potatoes peeled and chopped
1/2 tbsp oil
1 medium (140 g) carrot grated or finely diced
1/2 medium-large onion chopped
3 garlic cloves minced
1 cup (180 g) peas frozen or canned
1 tsp curry powder
1 tsp onion powder
1/2 tsp ground cumin
1/4 tsp ground nutmeg
3/4-1 tsp sea salt or less/more to taste
1/4 tsp smoked paprika
Red pepper flakes to taste
Black pepper to taste
1/4 cup (60 ml) vegetable broth
5 oz (140 g) vegan cheese of choice
Taco seasoning to sprinkle on top of taquitos (optional)
8-10 small/medium tortillas
